  <diagram name="Seite-1" id="m4YvLFaYmH49telENmWP">
    <mxGraphModel dx="3166" dy="1180" grid="1" gridSize="10" guides="1" tooltips="1" connect="1" arrows="1" fold="1" page="1" pageScale="1" pageWidth="827" pageHeight="1169" math="0" shadow="0">
      <root>
        <mxCell id="0" />
        <mxCell id="1" parent="0" />
        <UserObject label="" plantUmlData="{&#xa;  &quot;data&quot;: &quot;@startuml\ntitle Sequence Diagram – Scenario \&quot;Endstop Reached\&quot;\n\nautonumber\n\nactor \&quot;Mechanics / Actuator\&quot; as Mech\nparticipant \&quot;Endstop\\n(GPIO)\&quot; as Endstop\nparticipant \&quot;GPIO ISR\\n(IRAM)\&quot; as ISR\nparticipant \&quot;FaultLatch\&quot; as FaultLatch\nparticipant \&quot;Bts7960ActuatorDrive\&quot; as Drive\nparticipant \&quot;PWM / EN Hardware\&quot; as PwmHw\nparticipant \&quot;ControlTask\\n(periodic)\&quot; as ControlTask\nparticipant \&quot;PressController\&quot; as PressController\nparticipant \&quot;PressFsm\&quot; as PressFsm\nparticipant \&quot;MqttTask\&quot; as MqttTask\nparticipant \&quot;DisplayTask\&quot; as DisplayTask\n\nMech -&gt; Endstop : End position reached\nEndstop -&gt; ISR : GPIO interrupt\n\nactivate ISR\nISR -&gt; FaultLatch : latchEndstopFault()\nISR -&gt; Drive : emergencyStop()\nactivate Drive\nDrive -&gt; PwmHw : EN = 0\\nPWM = 0\nPwmHw --&gt; Drive : disabled\ndeactivate Drive\nISR --&gt; Endstop : interrupt acknowledged\ndeactivate ISR\n\n... until next control cycle ...\n\nControlTask -&gt; PressController : cycleTick(now)\nactivate PressController\n\nPressController -&gt; FaultLatch : readLatchedFault()\nFaultLatch --&gt; PressController : endstopFault = true\n\nPressController -&gt; PressFsm : step(inputs, endstopFault, now)\nactivate PressFsm\nPressFsm --&gt; PressController : transitionTo(ABORT_LATCH)\\noutput = STOP\ndeactivate PressFsm\n\nPressController -&gt; Drive : apply(STOP)\nactivate Drive\nDrive -&gt; PwmHw : PWM = 0\\nEN = 0\nPwmHw --&gt; Drive : still safe\ndeactivate Drive\n\nPressController --&gt; ControlTask : state = ABORT_LATCH\ndeactivate PressController\n\nopt Status reporting\n    ControlTask -&gt; MqttTask : publishState(ABORT_LATCH,\\nreason = ENDSTOP_REACHED)\n    ControlTask -&gt; DisplayTask : showFault(\&quot;Endstop reached\&quot;)\nend\n\nnote over ISR, Drive\nSafety-critical immediate path:\nThe actuator is stopped directly inside the ISR.\nend note\n\nnote over ControlTask, PressFsm\nDeterministic processing:\nThe FSM handles and latches the fault\nin the next cyclic control step.\nend note\n\n@enduml&quot;,&#xa;  &quot;format&quot;: &quot;svg&quot;&#xa;}" id="rU6GQyp_aGA5asrHp-7C-3">
